00:47:50,090 --> 00:47:55,090
...where my cats will also probably put
a lot of fur on it...

847
00:47:55,090 --> 00:47:57,590
...or knock it down! No! Oh!

848
00:47:57,590 --> 00:48:00,790
They like to do that! Is it out of real glass?
It's kind of heavy.

849
00:48:00,790 --> 00:48:04,190
You've got to be a little bit careful!
But yeah, thank you guys so much!

850
00:48:04,190 --> 00:48:08,190
I love you guys! It's been an honor so far, so...

851
00:48:08,190 --> 00:48:11,690
...let's do our best together!
Thank you for this award!

852
00:48:11,690 --> 00:48:15,190
Who's the next one? Who's next? Who's next?

853
00:48:15,190 --> 00:48:18,190
Is it Ninomae Ina'nis?

854
00:48:18,190 --> 00:48:22,790
Me? Oh, let's see what my award could be!

855
00:48:22,790 --> 00:48:25,590
Most violent? Yikes! Most violent, definitely!
You do it to yourself!

856
00:48:25,590 --> 00:48:29,690
No, no! All right, my award is...

857
00:48:29,690 --> 00:48:33,390
...oh yes, oh yes, I already guessed!

858
00:48:33,390 --> 00:48:38,390
It is... Most Time Spent on the Floor Award!
Oh, that I believe!

859
00:48:38,390 --> 00:48:42,690
Congratulations! Thank you, thank you, thank you!

860
00:48:42,690 --> 00:48:46,690
I know you guys probably think I would
never get this award, but you know...

861
00:48:46,690 --> 00:48:50,690
...I worked so hard this year to stay on the floor!

862
00:48:50,690 --> 00:48:54,290
Very unprecedented! And uh, yeah,
not only did I stay on the floor...

863
00:48:54,290 --> 00:48:58,590
...I, you know, really did my best to practice
dancing and singing this year...

864
00:48:58,590 --> 00:49:02,190
...to perform well with you guys, and I hope
that you guys see that as well!

865
00:49:02,190 --> 00:49:06,190
Thank you so much for all your support!
I'll continue to do my best with these girls!

866
00:49:06,190 --> 00:49:10,190
Yeah! Myth! Myth! Myth!

867
00:49:10,190 --> 00:49:15,190
And last but not least... coming up next!
Oh, what could it be?

868
00:49:15,190 --> 00:49:19,090
Our sneezer! Little Caesar's sneezer!
The most sneezes-sneezer!

869
00:49:19,090 --> 00:49:24,090
Most sneezes in the Myth 5th Anniversary showcase!
Most blessed!

870
00:49:24,090 --> 00:49:28,090
Okay, well, actually, my trophy is for...

871
00:49:28,090 --> 00:49:31,990
...ta-da! Best Worst Luck Award!

872
00:49:31,990 --> 00:49:36,690
Especially in games where there are
microtransactions! Yeah!

873
00:49:36,690 --> 00:49:40,190
That's not so positive! I mean,
I've seen it happen in real time!

874
00:49:40,190 --> 00:49:44,190
But the dedication, the determination to pull
a signed card or not...

875
00:49:44,190 --> 00:49:48,190
...I'm not going to give up yet! Real quick,
I'm going to be very sappy.

876
00:49:48,190 --> 00:49:50,190
Well, okay, go ahead. I really liked that line,
'I'm not going to give up yet.'

877
00:50:00,247 --> 00:50:01,547
I'm not gonna give up yet, because...

878
00:50:01,547 --> 00:50:02,547
Because...

879
00:50:03,047 --> 00:50:05,347
I'd like to think that we're not gonna give up yet,

880
00:50:05,347 --> 00:50:07,647
because there's still so much that I want to do,

881
00:50:08,747 --> 00:50:10,747
the three of us together.

882
00:50:11,647 --> 00:50:12,547
Together!

883
00:50:13,047 --> 00:50:14,547
You know?

884
00:50:14,747 --> 00:50:18,247
And I didn't think that I would be here
five years from the start with you guys.

885
00:50:18,247 --> 00:50:19,247
Same!

886
00:50:19,247 --> 00:50:19,747
Yeah.

887
00:50:19,747 --> 00:50:21,247
I really thought I'd be out of here.

888
00:50:21,247 --> 00:50:22,247
Same!

889
00:50:23,247 --> 00:50:27,747
But now I can't see a future where I'm not here
with you guys, so for now...

890
00:50:27,747 --> 00:50:30,747
Oh, that's so nice! That's so...

891
00:50:30,747 --> 00:50:31,747
Oh shucks!

892
00:50:31,747 --> 00:50:32,247
Okay.

893
00:50:32,747 --> 00:50:34,747
So because of that, I'm not gonna give up yet.

894
00:50:34,747 --> 00:50:37,247
I don't want to give up yet, so let's do our best!

895
00:50:37,747 --> 00:50:38,747
Jingle jingle!

896
00:50:39,247 --> 00:50:41,247
Oh yeah, the wrapping-up music is playing!

897
00:50:41,247 --> 00:50:44,247
I'm just gonna start talking about nothing
because it annoys me when they play the jingle...

898
00:50:44,247 --> 00:50:45,247
...to tell me to stop.

899
00:50:45,447 --> 00:50:48,247
This morning I ate a bagel
and I had cream cheese on it.

900
00:50:48,247 --> 00:50:50,247
It was delicious, but it went over my macros!

901
00:50:50,747 --> 00:50:53,247
And so I'm in big trouble with my trainer,
but it's fine! It's fine!

902
00:50:54,247 --> 00:50:56,747
Anyway, you can't get rid of me!

903
00:50:57,247 --> 00:50:58,247
Alright!

904
00:50:58,747 --> 00:51:01,247
You can't get rid of any of us, hopefully!

905
00:51:01,247 --> 00:51:03,747
Everybody, all good things come to an end,
unfortunately...

906
00:51:05,247 --> 00:51:08,747
...but thank you so much to the Holo EN community
for supporting us continuously for five years!

907
00:51:09,747 --> 00:51:13,747
Thank you to the girls today and all the staff-san
that supported us also for this celebration...

908
00:51:14,747 --> 00:51:16,747
...who gave us the trophies!

909
00:51:16,747 --> 00:51:19,247
Yeah, once again, congratulations to us!

910
00:51:19,747 --> 00:51:21,747
To us! Of five years!

911
00:51:22,247 --> 00:51:24,247
Yay! Thank you!

912
00:51:24,247 --> 00:51:26,747
Thanks everyone! Bye bye!

913
00:51:27,747 --> 00:51:29,247
Bye bye! Peace!

914
00:51:29,747 --> 00:51:31,247
Thanks! Don't forget the merch!

915
00:51:31,247 --> 00:51:33,247
Buy the merch! Merch, please!

916
00:51:34,247 --> 00:51:36,247
The merch is out! Nice!

